gonna get us killed.

549
00:55:56.083 --> 00:55:57.208
I need more power.

550
00:55:57.291 --> 00:55:59.958
Disable the safety panel
so I can override the limiter.

551
00:56:00.041 --> 00:56:02.708
How? I'm a pilot.
not a meknek.

552
00:56:02.791 --> 00:56:04.916
Just rip out
the whole brain board.

553
00:56:10.416 --> 00:56:12.000
Everything okay up there?

554
00:56:12.083 --> 00:56:13.500
Perfect.

555
00:56:20.208 --> 00:56:22.958
I told you to strap in.
Always wear your seat belt.

556
00:56:32.375 --> 00:56:34.250
Take it easy up there!

557
00:56:40.625 --> 00:56:41.958
There we go.

558
00:58:13.791 --> 00:58:15.625
That doesn't look like a Hutt.

559
00:58:15.708 --> 00:58:18.416
This is Imperial Commander
Janu Coin.

560
00:58:18.500 --> 00:58:21.666
He's full of information and
ready to sing like a Yuzzum.

561
00:58:21.750 --> 00:58:23.416
Isn't that right. Coin?

562
00:58:23.500 --> 00:58:24.916
I demand
an attorney be present

563
00:58:25.000 --> 00:58:26.166
