564
00:58:26.833 --> 00:58:27.833
You see?

565
00:58:28.333 --> 00:58:30.041
He's full of secrets.

566
00:58:30.875 --> 00:58:32.666
You were supposed
to bring back Rotta.

567
00:58:33.791 --> 00:58:36.041
We had an arrangement
with the Twins.

568
00:58:36.125 --> 00:58:38.208
This is your Ace of Staves.

569
00:58:38.958 --> 00:58:40.958
This is who they were
going to lead you to.

570
00:58:41.666 --> 00:58:42.791
And then tip him off.

571
00:58:42.875 --> 00:58:45.500
