for a very long time.

575
00:58:58.416 --> 00:58:59.916
and you crossed them.

576
00:59:01.375 --> 00:59:03.166
The Twins can hold a grudge.

577
00:59:03.250 --> 00:59:04.500
I made a call.

578
00:59:04.583 --> 00:59:06.208
I got you the big prize.

579
00:59:06.750 --> 00:59:08.708
The Twins can rot in hell.

580
00:59:08.791 --> 00:59:10.166
Well. you missed out
on them paying you

581
00:59:10.250 --> 00:59:12.208
