582
00:59:12.291 --> 00:59:13.416
Hmm...

583
00:59:13.500 --> 00:59:14.791
So be it.

584
00:59:16.791 --> 00:59:18.833
Well. I'll see if
I can hit up Command

585
00:59:18.916 --> 00:59:20.833
