for the capture of Coin.

586
00:59:20.916 --> 00:59:23.416
Don't worry about it.
It's on me.

587
00:59:24.208 --> 00:59:25.791
This one got messy.

588
00:59:25.875 --> 00:59:27.125
I'm taking a break.

589
00:59:28.708 --> 00:59:30.041
I understand.

590
00:59:31.083 --> 00:59:32.291
Mando.

591
00:59:34.958 --> 00:59:36.208
Good job.

592
01:01:00.583 --> 01:01:02.583
We're gonna
pull the restrictor plates.

593
01:01:02.666 --> 01:01:05.333
The first one should be
just past the return line.

594
01:01:05.416 --> 01:01:06.916
That's it.

595
01:01:07.000 --> 01:01:09.125
