that doesn't make her go.

603
01:01:43.833 --> 01:01:44.833
Hey!

604
01:01:44.916 --> 01:01:46.250
- Hey. Hey.

605
01:01:46.333 --> 01:01:47.333
No. don't touch me!

606
01:01:47.416 --> 01:01:49.750
Heel.

607
01:01:49.833 --> 01:01:51.541
