- The bad baby.

608
01:01:51.625 --> 01:01:53.583
Stay.

609
01:01:53.666 --> 01:01:55.000
I purged the fuel lines.

610
01:01:55.083 --> 01:01:56.750
I wanna remove
all the restrictors

611
01:01:56.833 --> 01:01:58.416
