616
01:02:11.166 --> 01:02:13.250
All right. Go.

617
01:02:19.875 --> 01:02:21.000
Don't worry about him.

618
01:02:23.375 --> 01:02:25.125
Little guy's gonna be okay.

619
01:02:27.291 --> 01:02:29.291
Sorry. I found these
in your kitchen.

620
01:02:33.125 --> 01:02:34.916
I was alone
when I was his age.

621
01:02:35.791 --> 01:02:37.333
I had to fend for myself.

622
01:02:42.708 --> 01:02:43.958
He's lucky he has you.

623
01:02:44.833 --> 01:02:47.708
Well. you didn't
turn out half bad.

624
01:02:49.125 --> 01:02:52.750
Mmm. Life's messy.
but we do the best we can.

625
01:02:54.333 --> 01:02:56.000
Listen. I called a gunrunner

626
