641
01:05:50.291 --> 01:05:51.291
Oh. What? Uh.

642
01:05:51.375 --> 01:05:52.708
- Wake up.
- What's going on?

643
01:05:52.791 --> 01:05:54.041
There's someone out there.

644
01:05:54.125 --> 01:05:55.583
