- We got a ship.

741
01:25:15.500 --> 01:25:16.958
That way. Let's go!

742
01:25:23.583 --> 01:25:27.333
Send the droids!
Release the Amani! Don't let him escape!

743
01:25:53.000 --> 01:25:54.791
This way. This way. yeah.

744
01:26:06.875 --> 01:26:08.666
This way!

745
01:26:15.083 --> 01:26:16.833
Up. up. up. up. going up!

746
01:26:16.916 --> 01:26:18.833
I don't want to fall.
I don't want to.

747
01:26:19.541 --> 01:26:20.541
Go!

748
01:26:20.625 --> 01:26:22.750
Yeah. Okay. okay. Yeah.
Let's go.

749
01:26:35.583 --> 01:26:37.958
Go. kid.
I can't fit in that thing.

750
01:26:39.250 --> 01:26:41.000
but you have to leave.

751
01:26:43.541 --> 01:26:44.750
Don't worry.

752
01:26:45.375 --> 01:26:47.083
I'll be right behind you.

753
01:26:51.250 --> 01:26:53.666
Go now. I'll hold them off.

754
01:26:54.208 --> 01:26:56.125
We'll come back
for you. Mando.

755
01:26:59.958 --> 01:27:01.208
Come on. baby.

756
01:27:01.291 --> 01:27:03.166
Don't worry. We'll be back.

757
01:27:03.250 --> 01:27:05.500
Yeah. let's go. Let's go.

758
01:27:05.583 --> 01:27:06.750
Come on. baby.

759
01:28:05.291 --> 01:28:06.625
-

760
01:28:22.916 --> 01:28:25.791
-

