01:40:39.875 --> 01:40:41.458
right now
is make him comfortable.

797
01:40:42.416 --> 01:40:45.583
There comes a time where
we all have to say goodbye.

798
01:40:52.833 --> 01:40:55.250
I wish you luck.
small traveler.

799
01:43:43.000 --> 01:43:44.041
Hey. kiddo.

800
01:43:49.833 --> 01:43:51.166
The old protect the young.

801
01:43:51.250 --> 01:43:53.041
and then the young
protect the old.

802
01:43:54.166 --> 01:43:55.500
This is the Way.

803
01:43:58.666 --> 01:44:00.333
Now how do we
get off this planet?

804
01:44:07.500 --> 01:44:10.041
That's the gunrunner
that was carrying Rotta.

805
01:45:17.708 --> 01:45:20.708
-

806
01:45:33.291 --> 01:45:34.458
-

807
01:46:24.708 --> 01:46:28.416
Well. kid. the way I see it
we got two choices.

808
01:46:29.125 --> 01:46:31.583
We can use this ship.
Get off world.

809
01:46:32.250 --> 01:46:34.750
That might buy us some time.
A little bit of peace.

810
01:46:35.250 --> 01:46:37.458
But the Hutts
will keep coming for us.

811
01:46:38.541 --> 01:46:40.291
Just like they came for Rotta.

812
01:46:43.416 --> 01:46:44.500
So. do we run?

813
01:46:48.791 --> 01:46:49.875
Or do we fight?

814
01:47:33.875 --> 01:47:35.666
- Huh?

815
01:47:51.583 --> 01:47:53.375
Repel the intruders!

816
01:47:53.458 --> 01:47:54.958
Roger. roger!

817
01:47:55.625 --> 01:47:57.041
Protect the palace!

818
01:47:57.125 --> 01:47:58.041
Affirmative.

819
01:48:07.583 --> 01:48:08.708
Follow my lead.

820
01:48:13.125 --> 01:48:14.208
Fire!

821
01:48:25.166 --> 01:48:26.750
Come on. Come on.

822
01:49:05.500 --> 01:49:07.041
On me.

823
01:49:50.708 --> 01:49:51.708
Fall back!

824
01:52:28.250 --> 01:52:30.333
Wait! We know much.

825
01:52:30.416 --> 01:52:31.916
Go help Rotta.

826
01:52:35.208 --> 01:52:37.750
-

827
01:52:40.125 --> 01:52:41.666
You saw my face.

828
01:52:42.583 --> 01:52:43.333
Stop!

829
01:52:44.333 --> 01:52:45.833
Now it's time to die.

830
01:53:49.208 --> 01:53:51.375
-

831
01:53:54.875 --> 01:53:55.958
Leave him alone!

832
01:54:18.125 --> 01:54:20.916
You don't have Jabba to protect you.

833
01:54:21.500 --> 01:54:22.958
I'm not little anymore!

834
01:55:54.208 --> 01:55:57.458
Stop! You'll kill us all!

835
01:56:42.000 --> 01:56:43.541
Save us. bounty hunter!

836
01:56:44.916 --> 01:56:45.916
Keibu.

837
01:56:46.000 --> 01:56:47.666
Save us!

838
01:56:53.375 --> 01:56:55.125
-

839
01:57:22.000 --> 01:57:24.666
We don't have much time.
We have to get out of here.

840
01:57:25.625 --> 01:57:26.833
Is there another way out?

841
01:57:26.916 --> 01:57:29.583
- I think it's that way.
- Go. Go!

842
01:57:46.083 --> 01:57:47.000
Target sighted.

843
01:58:13.000 --> 01:58:13.916
Hello?

844
01:58:14.000 --> 01:58:15.875
<i>Mando! We came back.</i>

845
01:58:15.958 --> 01:58:17.208
- What?
- We came back.

846
01:58:17.291 --> 01:58:19.000
We told you we would.

847
01:58:26.041 --> 01:58:29.000
<i>Adelphi Squadron.</i>
<i>entering atmosphere.</i>

848
01:58:29.958 --> 01:58:32.666
- What's your status. Mando?
<i>- We're under attack.</i>

849
01:58:33.666 --> 01:58:35.000
There are too many.

850
01:58:35.083 --> 01:58:37.083
Fire everything you have
at my location.

851
01:58:38.625 --> 01:58:41.833
<i>- Your location?</i>
- Yes. my location.

852
01:58:41.916 --> 01:58:43.416
I can't give that order.

853
01:58:43.500 --> 01:58:44.916
Don't worry...

854
01:58:46.916 --> 01:58:49.125
we'll be out of here
by the time you do.

855
01:58:50.750 --> 01:58:51.791
Good luck.

856
01:58:55.375 --> 01:58:56.666
Blue Leader to squadron.

857
01:58:57.250 --> 01:59:00.291
<i>assume defensive formation.</i>
<i>prepare to engage.</i>

858
01:59:00.375 --> 01:59:01.541
All weapons hot.

859
01:59:01.625 --> 01:59:02.458
Copy that.

860
01:59:20.083 --> 01:59:21.833
Enemy fighters approaching.

861
01:59:24.000 --> 01:59:24.875
Here they come.

862
01:59:52.166 --> 01:59:53.500
Turbolasers. up ahead.

863
01:59:53.583 --> 01:59:54.750
Got it.

864
02:00:15.625 --> 02:00:17.041
I've got one on my tail.

865
02:00:19.750 --> 02:00:21.250
I got you.

866
02:00:31.416 --> 02:00:33.041
- Yippee! Yay!

867
02:00:33.125 --> 02:00:34.708
Taking out the launch tubes.

868
02:00:42.458 --> 02:00:45.333
Blue Leader to Red Jammer.
mark it and lock it in.

869
02:00:47.833 --> 02:00:48.958
Locking in target.

870
02:00:52.666 --> 02:00:53.708
It's a dead end.

871
02:00:55.000 --> 02:00:56.416
We're trapped.

872
02:00:57.125 --> 02:00:58.333
Stand back.

873
02:01:04.708 --> 02:01:06.041
<i>We're closing fast.</i>

874
02:01:06.125 --> 02:01:07.541
Repeat. we're closing fast.

875
02:01:07.625 --> 02:01:09.208
You better be
out of there. Mando.

876
02:01:09.291 --> 02:01:10.708
Jump.

877
02:01:10.791 --> 02:01:12.875
That's a long way down.

878
02:01:12.958 --> 02:01:14.166
Closing on target.

879
02:01:15.708 --> 02:01:18.000
- Gotta jump.
- Moat's not that deep.

880
02:01:18.083 --> 02:01:20.125
It's a bomber. Jump.

881
02:01:20.208 --> 02:01:22.000
Let's light up this swamp.

882
02:01:56.791 --> 02:01:58.416
<i>Anybody got eyes on Mando?</i>

883
02:01:59.083 --> 02:02:00.083
There they are.

884
02:02:04.500 --> 02:02:08.250
Zeb. go collect the trash.

885
02:02:16.375 --> 02:02:19.166
I'm getting a little tired
of these hot extractions.

886
02:02:20.083 --> 02:02:22.041
What took you so long?

887
02:02:23.375 --> 02:02:24.500
Hop in.

888
02:02:24.583 --> 02:02:26.416
Let's head home.

889
02:02:49.333 --> 02:02:50.708
Colonel.

890
02:02:53.041 --> 02:02:54.416
Messy.

891
02:02:55.000 --> 02:02:56.250
Very messy.

892
02:02:57.458 --> 02:02:59.083
Why'd you come for me?

893
02:02:59.166 --> 02:03:00.666
That wasn't part
of the mission.

894
02:03:01.416 --> 02:03:04.541
You were right.
Coin told us everything.

895
02:03:05.041 --> 02:03:06.666
The Twins were playing us.

896
02:03:06.750 --> 02:03:09.291
Feeding information
to the Empire all along.

897
02:03:10.625 --> 02:03:13.291
They picked a side.
It wasn't ours.

898
02:03:13.916 --> 02:03:17.541
Besides.
we don't leave our own behind.

899
02:03:18.083 --> 02:03:19.875
I'm an independent contractor.

900
02:03:19.958 --> 02:03:22.916
Sure. Mando. Sure you are.

901
02:03:33.583 --> 02:03:35.500
Can I give you a ride
somewhere?

902
02:03:35.583 --> 02:03:37.791
Actually. I was thinking
I could stay here.

903
02:03:38.583 --> 02:03:40.375
Maybe work
for the New Republic.

904
02:03:40.958 --> 02:03:43.375
Don't take this
the wrong way. but...

905
02:03:43.458 --> 02:03:45.541
I'm not sure you would fit in.

906
02:03:45.625 --> 02:03:47.458
You know...

907
02:03:47.541 --> 02:03:49.791
...I might have
a uniform that would fit him.

908
02:03:50.833 --> 02:03:53.708
Come on.
let me buy you a drink.

909
02:03:55.500 --> 02:03:58.041
Thank you. Mando.
I owe you big time.

910
02:03:58.125 --> 02:03:59.458
Just doing my job.

911
02:04:00.083 --> 02:04:01.083
And keep an eye on him.

912
02:04:02.208 --> 02:04:03.833
Your dad's
one of the good ones.

913
02:04:18.291 --> 02:04:19.583
Come on. big guy.

914
02:04:20.750 --> 02:04:23.125
Watch your step.
First round's on me.

915
02:04:32.291 --> 02:04:34.416
Hey. kid. Come up here.

916
02:04:54.083 --> 02:04:55.291
Your turn.

917
02:04:58.208 --> 02:04:59.208
Go ahead.

917
02:05:00.305 --> 02:06:00.288
